    <Label name="lblInstructions" id="31afbc00-d448-4096-8109-df22893d766e">
        <caption>Enter the text to include or exclude.  The system first checks if the message starts with the include text.  If the message is included or no includes have been specified then it is checked against the exclude text.  Note that the time is removed before the message is checked.</caption>
